testsuite.name: ProverbTest
testsuite.system-out: For want of a nail the shoe was lost. For want of a shoe the horse was lost. And all for the want of a nail. For want of a nail the shoe was lost. For want of a shoe the horse was lost. For want of a horse the rider was lost. For want of a rider the message was lost. For want of a message the battle was lost. For want of a battle the kingdom was lost. And all for the want of a nail. And all for the want of a nail. For want of a nail the shoe was lost. And all for the want of a nail. For want of a pin the gun was lost. For want of a gun the soldier was lost. For want of a soldier the battle was lost. And all for the want of a pin.
